cal-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c21f8808-2334-4e60-a047-27a52e8adbce/11.png,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c21f8808-2334-4e60-a047-27a52e8adbce/12.png,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c21f8808-2334-4e60-a047-27a52e8adbce/13.png,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c21f8808-2334-4e60-a047-27a52e8adbce/14.png,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c21f8808-2334-4e60-a047-27a52e8adbce/15.png,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c21f8808-2334-4e60-a047-27a52e8adbce/16.png,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c21f8808-2334-4e60-a047-27a52e8adbce/17.png"}],"authors":[{"id":"d48811ba9b","name":"朱洪霞"},{"id":"de64cf7aeb","name":"戴行江"}]},"publication_details":{"c21f8808-2334-4e60-a047-27a52e8adbce":{"comments":[{"id":"da9f93c69c","publicationId":"c21f8808-2334-4e60-a047-27a52e8adbce","articleId":"5202e55cdb","index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"中共武汉市委材料组，一九七六年十二月"}],"contents":[{"id":"07d9e40f1b","type":"title","text":"三月八日朱洪霞在武重俱乐部集会上的讲话（节录）","index":0,"publicationId":"c21f8808-2334-4e60-a047-27a52e8adbce","articleId":"5202e55cdb"},{"id":"7947495986","type":"paragraph","text":"朱洪霞在会上介绍了所谓河南的经验，他说：“河南来的姓唐的说：毛主席说，支持革命造反派，对造反派要高抬贵手，对压制革命造反派的要赶下台，城市的要赶到农村去’。河南的造反派已经组织起来了，抵制了党内的走资派，现在已经轰轰烈烈地搞起来了……”。","index":1,"publicationId":"c21f8808-2334-4e60-a047-27a52e8adbce","articleId":"5202e55cdb"},{"id":"6e8154d2ec","type":"paragraph","text":"戴行江说：“我这次准备掉脑袋，也要干到底。我们打算把王福魁（武重党委书记）的讲话收集起来进行批判，要把王轰下台。我们要听夏邦银、谢望春的指挥。他们要我们冲就冲，要我们打就打，要我们杀就杀。夏邦银、谢望春要我们把火点得旺一些。团结起来，共同战斗。胜利一定属于我们的。”","index":2,"publicationId":"c21f8808-2334-4e60-a047-27a52e8adbce","articleId":"5202e55cdb"},{"id":"03eb5bbd7c","type":"paragraph","text":"朱洪霞还说：“我们过去错过了三次机会，一次是陈再道下台，一次是刘丰下台，一次是批林批孔。现在走资派还在走，革命造反派就要斗。”","index":3,"publicationId":"c21f8808-2334-4e60-a047-27a52e8adbce","articleId":"5202e55cdb"},{"id":"22b9e4136e","type":"paragraph","text":"会议开始前，散发了二十条“口号报”，恶毒攻击李先念副总理和省委领导同志。","index":4,"publicationId":"c21f8808-2334-4e60-a047-27a52e8adbce","articleId":"5202e55cdb"}],"page":{"id":"6dde8b7331","publicationId":"c21f8808-2334-4e60-a047-27a52e8adbce","articleId":"5202e55cdb","start":7,"end":7}}}},"__N_SSG":true}